From: Brian Cain <bcain@quicinc.com>
Date: Thu, 24 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Gate ELD test/ and Plugins/ on LLVM_INCLUDE_TESTS

When LLVM_INCLUDE_TESTS is OFF, skip building ELD's test and plugin
targets.  These MODULE libraries link against libLW and would otherwise
be exported into LLVMExports.cmake, creating problems for cross-builds.
---
 CMakeLists.txt | 6 ++++--
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -197,7 +197,9 @@
 add_subdirectory(lib)
 add_subdirectory(tools)
 add_subdirectory(docs)
-add_subdirectory(test)
-add_subdirectory(Plugins)
+if(LLVM_INCLUDE_TESTS)
+  add_subdirectory(test)
+  add_subdirectory(Plugins)
+endif()

 option(ELD_INSTALL_LINKER_SCRIPT_TEMPLATES "Include linker script templates in the install" ON)
--
